       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI29202.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI29202.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Manutençăo perfis năo Master                               *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI29202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD2000 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV2920.
       COPY ARCV2921.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-ARVT2002 PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARVT2002'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(08) VALUE 'ARI29202'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI29202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV2920-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV2920-ASE               TO ARCV2921-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV2920-ADE       TO ARCV2921-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-PERFILMASTER
                 THRU 2199-OBTEM-PERFILMASTER-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-PERFILMASTER
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-PERFILMASTER.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-PERFILMASTER' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-ORIGEM        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  VIAL0001-ORIGEM          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Só pode existir um perfil master por cliente

           MOVE ARCK0002-PERFILMAST-CLIENT TO ARCD2000-INDPERM
           MOVE VIAL0001-ORIGEM            TO ARCD2000-APLIC

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       CPERFIL
                 INTO
                       :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
                 FROM ARVT2002_INFPERFIL
                 WHERE
                      INDPERM = :ARCD2000-INDPERM
                      AND APLIC = :ARCD2000-APLIC
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT2002               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE ARCD2000-CPERFIL     TO ARCV2920-CPERFILM
                                              ARCV2921-CPERFILM
              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2 TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2  TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-OBTEM-PERFILMASTER-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-OBTEM-DADOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-OBTEM-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV2920-CPERFIL           TO ARCD2000-CPERFIL
           MOVE ARCK0002-N-PERFIL-MASTER   TO ARCD2000-INDPERM
           MOVE ARCV2921-CPERFILM          TO ARCD2000-CPERFILM

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       CPERFIL
                     , GDESCRICAO
                 INTO
                       :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
                     , :ARCD2000-GDESCRICAO
                 FROM ARVT2002_INFPERFIL
                 WHERE
                    CPERFIL = :ARCD2000-CPERFIL
                    AND INDPERM = :ARCD2000-INDPERM
                    AND CPERFILM = :ARCD2000-CPERFILM
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-ARVT2002               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV2921-CPERFIL-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-CPERFIL-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV2921-CPERFIL-MSG
                    MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                      TO ARCV2921-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
                 ELSE
                    MOVE ARCD2000-CPERFIL
                      TO ARCV2921-CPERFIL
                    MOVE ARCD2000-GDESCRICAO
                      TO ARCV2921-GDESCRICAO
                    IF NOT VIAL0001-VISUALIZACAO
                        CONTINUE
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO ARCV2921-CPERFIL-S
                    MOVE ARCK0001-CPERFIL-N-EXISTS
                      TO ARCV2921-CPERFIL-MSG
                    MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR
                      TO ARCV2921-CPERFIL-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2299-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ARCV2921-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE ARCV2921-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV2921-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
